text: After coming to Singapore for a month, I looked for a nearby Korean church and ended up holding a service here. It was full of the grace of the Word and praise, and the meal fellowship system after the service was also great🥰 I will support you even when I return to Korea so that God’s grace will be even more abundant in the Word of Life Church🙌

I visited during my travels and worshiped.
I am receiving great challenges through gracious praise and words.
The praise team praise is gracious.
